0:00:00.020,0:00:02.160
Emanueri! (Mwari Anesu - Mateo 1:23)

0:00:02.160,0:00:04.260
Rumbidzai Ishe, Chechi!

0:00:04.260,0:00:07.540
Zita rangu ndi Ogbonna Iwuogbonnaya.

0:00:07.540,0:00:12.460
Ini ndinobva ku Abia State, Nigeria, ndichigara ku Libya.

0:00:12.460,0:00:19.040
Uchapupu hwangu hwakaita sezvizvi: Ini ndinosha sa werudha wegasi .

0:00:19.040,0:00:23.360
Rimwe zuva, mutengi akandiunzira chinhu chekugadzira muchitoro changu.

0:00:23.360,0:00:32.820
Apo ndakatanga basa, ndakanga ndatoongorora kuti ndione kana gasi raishanda zvakanaka.

0:00:32.820,0:00:37.640
Zvisinei, pakarepo pandakatanga kushanda, gasi rakaputika.

0:00:37.640,0:00:42.000
Apo rakaputika, ndakanga ndisingazivi zvakare kuti ndaive kupi.

0:00:42.000,0:00:49.080
Ndakanga ndavhiringidzika kusvika pamwero wekuti ndakanga ndisingagone kusvinudza meso angu.

0:00:49.080,0:00:54.620
Ndakadana mutyairi wangu akanditora kuchipatara chisiri che hurumende.

0:00:54.620,0:01:05.160
Patakasvika ikoko, vakati havaikwanisa kuita chero chinhu uye vakandiratidza kune chipatara chandaifanira kuenda.

0:01:05.160,0:01:15.680
Pandakazosvika ikoko, ndakasangana nevazvarwa veku Libya vaipfuura vashanu vaive vagere vaine nyaya dzakasiyana siyana .

0:01:15.680,0:01:21.340
Pashure pokumirira kwemaminitsi makumi matatu, ndakaudza mutyairi wangu kuti taifanira kubva.

0:01:21.340,0:01:28.120
Mutyairi wacho akavhiringidzika ndokubvunza kuti sei nokuti aiziva kuti ndaive mumarwadzo makuru kuru.

0:01:28.120,0:01:34.140
Handaikwanisa kugara pasi kana kubata chiso changu nokuti kurwadziwa kwaiva kwakanyanya kwandiri.

0:01:34.140,0:01:40.620
Handaikwanisi kutsungirira kurwadziwa kwacho saka ndakaudza mutyairi wangu kuti taifanira kuenda.

0:01:40.620,0:01:45.400
Iwe unoreva pawakatorwa kuenda kuchipatara chekutanga, wakanyatsorambwa?

0:01:45.400,0:01:46.060
Hongu

0:01:46.060,0:01:49.440
Nokuti chiso chako chakanga chaparadzwa zvachose, chakatsva?

0:01:49.440,0:01:50.189
Ndizvo chaizvo.

0:01:50.189,0:01:51.760
Uye vakakoniwa kukubatsira?

0:01:51.760,0:01:52.640
Ndizvo chaizvo.

0:01:52.640,0:01:55.180
Kubva ipapo, wakatorwa kuenda kuchipatara chechipiri?

0:01:55.180,0:01:55.880
Hongu

0:01:55.880,0:01:59.940
Pawakasvika ikoko, pakanga pasina vanachiremba vekuti vakubatsire panyaya yako.

0:01:59.940,0:02:00.920
Ndizvo chaizvo.

0:02:00.920,0:02:02.280
Saka chii chakaitika kubva ipapo?

0:02:02.280,0:02:09.380
Kubva ipapo, ndakarangarira kuti ndaiva ne Morning Water mumba mangu; Ndaiwanzoona Emmanuel TV.

0:02:09.380,0:02:16.280
Ndakanga ndaona Mwari achishandisa mu Porofita T.B. Joshua kuporesa vanhu vazhinji.

0:02:16.280,0:02:20.820
Ndakasarudza kudzokera kumba kwangu.

0:02:20.820,0:02:26.540
Marwadzo aive akanyanya zvokuti ndaisaziva kuti ndaive kupi.

0:02:26.540,0:02:31.960
Marwadzo acho aive akanyanya zvokuti ndakanga ndisingagoni kunyange kubata chiso changu.

0:02:31.960,0:02:36.640
Vanhu vanopfuura vashanu vakanga vachindifefedza kunyange zvazvo ndakanga ndiri muimba yaive ne mhepo inotonhorera.

0:02:36.640,0:02:38.840
Iwe unoreva kuti manzwiro emarwadzo ekutsva aive akanyanya?

0:02:38.840,0:02:39.700
Zvakanyanyisa.

0:02:39.700,0:02:41.480
Zvekuti waitadza kubata chiso chako?

0:02:41.480,0:02:42.400
Kana kana.

0:02:42.400,0:02:43.380
Waitadza kuzarura maziso ako?

0:02:43.380,0:02:51.220
Handaikwanisa kuzarura maziso angu; Ndakatofunga kuti maziso angu akanga apofomadzwa.

0:02:51.220,0:02:52.300
Iwe waifunga kuti iwe wakange wave bofu?

0:02:52.300,0:02:54.760
Ndaifunga kuti ndakanga ndapofomadzwa.

0:02:54.760,0:03:03.020
Pandakashandisa Morning Water pachiso changu, pakarepo maziso angu akavhurika!

0:03:03.020,0:03:08.340
Ndakati, "Chii ichi?"

0:03:08.340,0:03:15.220
Saka, nguva yokutanga yawakashumira Morning Water kumeso kwako, iwe wakabva wagona kuvhura maziso ako zvakajeka?

0:03:15.220,0:03:16.340
Ndizvo zvauri kutaura here?

0:03:16.340,0:03:24.320
Paiva apo ndakashandisa Morning Water kekutanga apo ndakakwanisa kuona zvakanga zvaitika kwandiri.

0:03:24.320,0:03:28.600
Pakarepo mushure mekushumira Morning Water, ndakatora girazi ndikazvitarisa.

0:03:28.600,0:03:31.760
Ndakati, "O Mwari!" Ndakatenda Mwari.

0:03:31.760,0:03:42.000
Ndakaramba ndichishumira Morning Water uye zvishoma nezvishoma, ndisingatori mishonga,

0:03:42.000,0:03:45.700
chiso changu chakatanga kusvuuka ne kuoma.

0:03:45.700,0:03:51.600
Isa maoko ako pamwechete kuna Kristu Jesu!

0:03:51.600,0:03:53.860
Zvechokwadi, tiri kushumira Mwari muhombe.

0:03:53.860,0:03:57.680
Tinoda kuti iwe utiratidze - tirikuona mifananidzo pa bhodhi riri pedyo newe.

0:03:57.680,0:04:01.920
Iwe ungatiudza here kuti zvifananidzo izvi zvinomirirei.

0:04:01.920,0:04:08.080
Apa ndipo pazvakaitika.

0:04:08.080,0:04:14.040
Pa screen yeterevhizheni yedu, tiri kuona mufananidzo weapo chiitiko chacho chakaitika - apo akatsva.

0:04:14.040,0:04:20.580
Apo ndakatanga kushumira Morning Water, chiso changu chakatanga kusvuuka, ndini uyu.

0:04:20.580,0:04:25.600
Saka ndipo apo ganda rakatsva rakatanga kusvuuka, mushure mekushumira kwe Morning Water?

0:04:25.600,0:04:26.100
Hongu

0:04:26.100,0:04:33.920
Ndakatofunga kuti ganda rangu raisazo tsvedzerera zvakare sezvandakaona vamwe vakatarisana nedambudziko rakafanana

0:04:33.920,0:04:38.040
vazhinji vavo vakafa kana kuti chiso chavo chakatukwa.

0:04:38.040,0:04:44.860
Kuna Mwari ngakuve nekubwinya, kuburikidza ne Morning Water, kumeso kwangu kwakave sezvizvi

0:04:44.860,0:04:49.160
zvishoma zvishoma ndiri pano zvino; Ini ndiri uchapupu hupenyu!

0:04:49.160,0:04:56.060
Ndakatosiya ndebvu dzangu kuti dzikure nokuti handina kumbofunga kuti ndaizomera nendebvu zvakare.

0:04:56.060,0:04:58.100
Iwe wati chii? Ndapota dzokorora zvakare zvawataura.

0:04:58.100,0:05:05.220
Ndakatosiya ndebvu dzangu kuti dzikure nokuti handina kumbofunga kuti ndaizomera nendebvu zvakare.

0:05:05.220,0:05:10.500
Isa maoko ako pamwechete kuna Kristu Jesu!

0:05:10.500,0:05:19.340
Chokwadi, tinogona kufungidzira! Ndebvu dzingamere sei zvakare pameso pakatsva? - Hakuna zvakadaro.

0:05:19.340,0:05:22.000
Changamire, tinoda kukubvunza mubvunzo umwe zvakare:

0:05:22.000,0:05:28.540
Dai pakanga pasina Morning Water, iwe unofunga kuti chii chingadai chakaitika kune chiso chako

0:05:28.540,0:05:30.800
chatiri kuona chichipenya zvino?

0:05:30.800,0:05:34.720
Ndingadai ndakavhiyiwa kuti ndingadziriswe.

0:05:34.720,0:05:37.440
Asi kuna Mwari ngakuve ne kubwinya, chii chakaitika kune chiso chako?

0:05:37.440,0:05:43.480
Ndinotenda Mwari zvakanyanya nokuti ndiri nani ikozvino uye ndakasimba. Kunyange ruoko rwangu rwakapiswa rwakanaka ikozvino.

0:05:43.480,0:05:45.120
Zvinhu zvose zvakadzorerwa zvachose?

0:05:45.120,0:05:45.880
Hongu

0:05:45.880,0:05:52.320
Kuna Mwari ngakuve kubwinya. Ngatiisei maoko edu pamwe kuna Kristu Jesu!

0:05:52.320,0:05:57.760
Chii chaunoda kutaura zvino nezve zodzo rakasimba se Morning Water yakashandiswa na Mwari Wamasimba Ose

0:05:57.760,0:06:01.920
kudzosera ganda rako ne kuritsiva ne raivepo pakutanga?

0:06:01.920,0:06:14.780
Ndaiwanzoudza vanhu kuti Mwari akatumira Morning Water kuburikidza ne mu Porofita T.B. Joshua kwatiri kuti tishandise.

0:06:14.780,0:06:20.560
Morning Water chinhu chandinoona zvakaoma kutsanangura.

0:06:20.560,0:06:29.940
Paiva nemukomana akauyiswa kumba kwangu ku Libya airwadziwa ne mudumbu.

0:06:29.940,0:06:34.880
Akange asingakwanisi kudya; iye aizobva arutsa chero chinhu chipi zvacho chaipinda mumuromo make.

0:06:34.880,0:06:45.620
Asi pandakashumira Morning Water kwaari, akabva angodya mabhisikiti ndokunwa.

0:06:45.620,0:06:50.880
Munguva duku, akakumbira mupunga - uyu aiva mukomana aisagona kudya kwemazuva matatu.

0:06:50.880,0:06:55.020
Chinhu chipi nechipi chaaisa mumuromo wake kare, aizorutsa pakarepo.

0:06:55.020,0:07:02.440
Saka, Morning Water chinhu chikuru Mwari Wemasimbaose akatumira kwatiri kuburikidza ne mu Porofita T.B. Joshua.

0:07:02.440,0:07:05.320
Kuna Mwari ngakuve kubwinya! Tinoziva kuti takakomborerwa.

0:07:05.320,0:07:11.680
Ndeapi mazano uwunawo zvino kune vatariri varikukuona nevaya varikuteerera ikozvino?

0:07:11.680,0:07:13.240
Rumbidzai Ishe!

0:07:13.240,0:07:19.760
Yambiro yangu kuvatariri, kunyanya kune avo vari kundiona kubva ku Libya -

0:07:19.760,0:07:34.580
Musi we Svondo hatifaniri kuenda kunoshanda ku Libya uye tinonamata nguva dzose neSCOAN -

0:07:34.580,0:07:42.120
Yambiro yandinayo kuvanhu ndeye kuti tendai kuna Mwari nokuti na Mwari, zvinhu zvose zvinogoneka.

0:07:42.120,0:07:51.360
Handina kutenda kare kuti ndaizove sezvizvi nhasi asi kuburikidza ne Emmanuel TV ne Morning Water,

0:07:51.360,0:07:56.160
Ndiri uchapupu hupenyu nhasi; Ndinotenda Mwari.

0:07:56.160,0:07:58.140
Ameni

0:07:58.140,0:08:00.620
Kekupedzisira ungabate kumeso kwako here?

0:08:00.620,0:08:03.020
Iwe wati waive usingagone kubata chiso chako kare.

0:08:03.020,0:08:07.000
Ndapota ungabate chiso chako uye utiudze kana uchiri kunzwa kurwadziwa here.

0:08:07.000,0:08:09.600
Hapana. Hapana marwadzo. Iye zvino ndanaka.

0:08:09.600,0:08:10.840
Uri kunzwa kurwadziwa here?

0:08:10.840,0:08:12.320
Hapana  kana. Ndiri zvakanaka.

0:08:12.320,0:08:13.620
Zvese zvitsva?

0:08:13.620,0:08:14.660
Zvese zvitsva?

0:08:14.660,0:08:16.860
Zvakanakisa, kupa mbiri kuna Mwari.

0:08:16.860,0:08:21.160
Isa maoko ako pamwechete kuna Kristu Jesu!

0:08:21.160,0:08:24.740
Tinotenda Mwari Wamasimba Ose nokuda kwe chapupu chakanakisisa icho wagoverana nesu.

0:08:24.740,0:08:30.220
Tinovimba izvi zvatikurudzira chaizvo uye zvasimudzira kutenda kwedu muna Kristu Jesu.

0:08:30.220,0:08:34.600
Tinoda kukukurudzira ikozvino kuti wasunungurwa, wakarapwa kuti kubwinya kupihwe kuna Mwari,

0:08:34.600,0:08:38.540
ramba uchirarama hupenyu hwako kufadza Jesu Kristu, uye tinonyengetera kuti Akupe nyasha dzeku

0:08:38.540,0:08:42.480
kuchengeta kurapwa kwakanakisa uku, muzita ra Jesu rine simba.

